# PINOUT
# 	https://www.microcontroller-project.com/rs485-communication-between-arduino-mega-and-arduino-pro-mini.html
# RS485		PI
# --------------------
# DI		TX
# DE		GPIO 26 (37)
# RE		GPIO 26 (37)
# RO		RX (10 UART0 RX)
#
#
# VCC		5V
# Gnd		Gnd
